1. Added Semantics element - <header>, <nav>, <section>, <form>, <footer>, <label>, <progress>
2. <audio> and </video> elements embed
3. Added new <input> types: email, password, search, url, text, number, button, checkbox, radio, range, 
   date, datetime, datetime-local, month, time, week, color(color-picker), tel(telephone number), file
4. Attributes: accept(filetypes), alt, autocomplete, autofocus, checked, disabled, 
   max, min, name, pattern, required, type, size
5. Attribute selectors - ::placeholder
6. Drag and drop
7. Device access using camera api
8. contentEditable
9. Regular expression - pattern attribute
10. async and defer attribute - <script async> and <script defer>
